係針對林鄭、唔針對政制，就會有雙普選？<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n#唔撤就罷<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買罷課<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港四罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#解散警隊<br />\n#永遠不光顧荃灣北角元朗商戶<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"01ba4ac476bbbd301c585720358b715d1ff0f11c","tid":1488383,"uid":193565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c65535a353a058d1173ec1d382f449468d327bc","tid":1488383,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a8f0b938ff772f0c915ecebb7bb6e3953e593c","tid":1488383,"uid":15010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:19:06.000Z","msg":"好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7211601f7aef3550c3bba854bcee09351ea22c","tid":1488383,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:19:19.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"03ee7a580624cf303111369b415956334db7f454","tid":1488383,"uid":263323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"828e15a75a5a183d7d14e87de3dc2ee524f5183a","tid":1488383,"uid":181318,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:12:12.000Z","msg":"出現左好耐一直冇研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:19:38.000Z","msg":"好值得大家駐足欣賞下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a2e52e06a3130eec6479a0a026c665b23c9550","tid":1488